title: [Commie] Teekyuu - 33 [207AB4C4].mkv
description: Description: Four girls make up Kameido High School`s Tennis Club, but they don`t actually get in much tennis practice. [Oshimoto Yuri] is the club`s only freshman and the only sane person in this collection of eccentric personalities. Each day is spent in fun with her sophomore seniors, [Shinjou Kanae], who is utterly inept at tennis, [Takamiya Nasuno], who attempts to solve every problem with money, and [Bandou Marimo], who, despite her elegant looks, is quite the pervert. ~ translated and adapted from official site by Cranston Note: The title is a wordplay on a Japanese term for tennis, teikyuu.
